The '''Cerean Quadrant''' was the region of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] that contained the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Cerea/Legends|Cerea]]. [[Ki-Adi-Mundi/Legends|Ki-Adi-Mundi]] was the [[Jedi Watchman/Legends|Jedi Watchman]] of the region,<ref name="Star Wars 8">[[Star Wars (1998) 8|''Star Wars'' (1998) 8]]</ref> as was his fellow [[Cerean/Legends|Cerean]] [[Tarr Seirr]].<ref name="DBTS">{{DB|character|tarrseirr|Seirr, Tarr}}</ref>

This quadrant was likely within [[Semagi sector/Legends|Semagi sector]].<ref name="TEAOC">{{SW|url=news/star-wars-the-essential-atlas-online-companion|text=''Star Wars: The Essential Atlas'' Online Companion|int=Star Wars: The Essential Atlas Online Companion}}</ref>

